Subject: Getting error: Page cannot be loaded
Description: User is able to open website - https://us.salesplanning.varicent.com/ and is also able to go to his own demo page - https://us.salesplanning.varicent.com/zs/zs-sean-demo/. however when he tries to access the tabs on that page he gets error ofPage cannot be loaded. On disabling EPP the pages get loaded properly. Uploading Logs while recreating the scenario and also uploading screenshots . Since we are not getting any logs for Content threat Blocked event so have whitelisted the below URL's with wild card: https://us.salesplanning.varicent.com/* https://us.salesplanning.varicent.com* Still user is not able to access. Please analyze logs and update us the status. Thanks Manpreet.
Solution_Comment__c: resolved by adding cognito-idp.us-east-1.amazonaws.com to whitelist.
